- Tu não, Langdon.

154
00:09:47,458 --> 00:09:48,832
Onde arranjaste esse lenço?

155
00:09:48,833 --> 00:09:49,916
Felicity?

156
00:09:50,833 --> 00:09:51,958
Amos?

157
00:09:53,583 --> 00:09:54,666
Felicity!

158
00:09:56,083 --> 00:09:57,416
