166
00:10:12,375 --> 00:10:14,374
ChumBar da Tia Cleo expirado.

167
00:10:14,375 --> 00:10:15,833
<i>Fiquei doente durante dias!</i>

168
00:10:16,125 --> 00:10:18,125
